## Simple PHP MVC Framework
### Was bored and wanted to write something..

### Requirements
docker
>> run docker-compose up
>> visit localhost:3000

### Migrations

#### Create migration
>> sudo docker exec mvc-app-1 vendor/bin/phinx  create TestMigration
>> Read more here https://hrportal.readthedocs.io/en/latest/commands.html

#### Development

>> sudo docker exec mvc-app-1 vendor/bin/phinx migrate  -e development

#### Production

>> sudo docker exec mvc-app-1 vendor/bin/phinx migrate  -e production

#### Seeding Data

>> sudo docker exec mvc-app-1 vendor/bin/phinx seed:create

>> sudo docker exec mvc-app-1 vendor/bin/phinx seed:run  -e development

### Credits
>> phinx - https://phinx.org/
>> Laravel ORM - https://laravel.com/docs/8.x/eloquent
